1
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,440
The sun today

2
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:43,450
seems exceptionally good.

3
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:44,400
Please.

4
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:45,880
Please save my daughter.

5
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,240
Mom's voice.

6
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:49,600
So it's not the sun.

7
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:51,520
It's the light in the operating room.

8
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:51,980
Shan Yu.

9
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:52,880
Don't give up.

10
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,160
Dad can sell the house

11
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:55,000
and the car.

12
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:56,160
As long as it saves you,

13
00:00:56,160 --> 00:00:57,200
I'll do anything.

14
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:57,680
Shan Yu.

15
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:58,620
Shan Yu.

16
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:00,040
You must hold on, Shan Yu.

17
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:00,640
Family members,

18
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,600
please don't interfere with the surgery.

19
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,160
Shan Yu,

20
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:04,000
don't leave Mom.

21
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,600
As long as you can stay alive.

22
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:06,200
Dandan.

23
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:08,360
Dandan.

24
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,720
Living,

25
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:12,400
can't I give up?

26
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:13,760
Then,

27
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:16,000
who can save me?

28
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:32,720
Where is this?

29
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,400
This is my consciousness space.

30
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,080
Welcome.

31
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,680
Who are you?

32
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,039
I...

33
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,000
I have no name.

34
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:44,600
But,

35
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,240
someone once called me

36
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,860
World Consciousness.

37
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,920
World consciousness.

38
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:54,160
I am a spiritual consciousness born from the origin of this world.

39
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,020
Since my birth,

40
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,740
countless years have passed.

41
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:57,880
Years ago,

42
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,530
I was destroyed by a villain born in this land.

43
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,840
The world collapsed,

44
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,480
leaving devastation everywhere.

45
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,640
The origin consumed itself

46
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,370
in an attempt to save the world.

47
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,080
Unfortunately,

48
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:11,680
I reversed time dozens of times but could not change the destined destruction.

49
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,600
The power of the origin

50
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:14,400
has been completely exhausted.

51
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,600
If I can't survive this time reversal,

52
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,200
I will cease to exist.

53
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,680
You too.

54
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:22,760
I hope

55
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,740
you can help me.

56
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,320
Me?

57
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,200
I can help you?

58
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:30,320
The guidance given by the origin as it was about to wither.

59
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,160
It told me

60
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:34,130
you would be the chance to continue the world.

61
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,000
So,

62
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,320
can you?

63
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,200
In return,

64
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,650
I can give you my remaining energy.

65
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:43,800
It should be enough to bring your body back to life.

66
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,240
Dandan.

67
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,760
Danyu.

68
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,520
Okay.

69
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,520
What's going on?

70
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,800
No way.

71
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,560
I got injured right after I arrived.

72
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,160
Isn't it a bit too miserable?

73
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,720
Your current identity

74
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:38,079
is on a mission with the Son of the World.

75
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,410
The Son of the World?

76
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,000
Yes.

77
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,440
His name is Wei Wuzhou,

78
00:03:41,440 --> 00:03:43,000
the son of the leader of Tianyan Sect.

79
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,880
Since birth,

80
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:46,160
he has gathered a trace of origin power

81
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,560
and enjoyed the fortune of Heavenly Dao.

82
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,600
As a proxy,

83
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,880
he has always been maintaining the stability of the world.

84
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,160
This sounds...

85
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:54,400
Why does he sound so much like a male lead in a web novel?

86
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,600
Then doesn't that mean

87
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,400
there should also be a female lead?

88
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,880
Only when the relationship between the son and daughter of the world is stable

89
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,480
will the world not be in turmoil.

90
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,960
So if you want to understand it that way,

91
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,890
that's fine too.

92
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,480
It hurts so much.

93
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,360
Danyu,

94
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,160
don't move yet.

95
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,480
You have been poisoned by the Nether Poison.

96
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,640
I'm poisoned?

97
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:11,320
Yes.

98
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,720
This is a unique skill of the Nether Demon.

99
00:04:13,720 --> 00:04:14,720
So,

100
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,810
there are demons in your world.

101
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,480
This is a world of gods and demons.

102
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,010
Of course there are demons.

103
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,200
Good thing

104
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:26,000
I brought the Panacea Pill Xiaoxue gave me.

105
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,160
What am I

106
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,000
here for?

107
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,440
To clean up demons

108
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,280
and stop the end of the world.

109
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:34,880
Do I look like I can beat them?

110
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,810
You will be fine.

111
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,540
These damn Nether Demons.

112
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,280
It's all my fault.

113
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,360
Since we're already here,

114
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,000
how would we know without trying?

115
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,960
F*ck.

116
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,400
He seems

117
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,810
to care about me so much.

118
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,530
Could he be in love with this identity?

119
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,820
That's not gonna work.

120
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,240
The male lead belongs to the female lead.

121
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,720
The main couple can't be separated.

122
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,380
Otherwise,

123
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,560
the world will be destroyed, right?

124
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,400
That's how it's written in novels.

125
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,440
I don't want to die before it even starts.

126
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:07,120
I'm still counting on completing the mission

127
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,600
to get a healthy body.

128
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,480
But

129
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,520
they are the male and female leads,

130
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,360
and I got injured as soon as I arrived.

131
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,680
Then doesn't that make me a cannon fodder?

132
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,480
I don't know if you are a cannon fodder.

133
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,280
As for him,

134
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,520
he is your brother.

135
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,520
So he's my brother.

136
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:24,880
Then it's fine.

137
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,920
I don't feel that bad anymore.

138
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:29,780
The poison in me seems to be cured.

139
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:30,880
Awesome.

140
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,560
Amazing.

141
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,200
Thank you.

142
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,720
Danyu,

143
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,440
what did you just say?

144
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,520
Thank you?

145
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:49,440
Danyu,

146
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,920
you've finally grown up.

147
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,800
Grown up?

148
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,320
How old is she, and she's still growing up?

149
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,040
Indeed,

150
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,320
people only grow through suffering.

151
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,680
Well...

152
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,640
Danyu,

153
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:02,560
your suffering this time was not in vain.

154
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,960
Either growing up or maturing.

155
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,360
What kind of adjectives are these?

156
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:05,690
Come.

157
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,320
Get up.

158
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,720
Wuzhou.

159
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,000
Are you guys okay?

160
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,640
Xiaoxue.

161
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,640
She is...

162
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:19,760
This

163
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,240
is the Daughter of the World,

164
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,800
the only daughter of the Master of Danyang Valley,

165
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,680
Mu Chenxue.

166
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,770
The heroine.

167
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,520
Xiaoxue.

168
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,080
Danyu.

169
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,360
She was poisoned by the Nether Poison.

170
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:28,840
But

171
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,320
thanks to your Antidote Pill,

172
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,200
she is fine.

173
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,120
The Daughter of the World has arrived.

174
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,800
My chosen team is assembled.

175
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,159
With their help,

176
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,890
our chances of saving the world are very high.

177
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,680
Eat this too.

178
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,640
It will clear the remaining poison

179
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,170
and restore your strength.

180
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,000
Thank you.

181
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,800
Why is Lu Danyu

182
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,730
acting differently today?

183
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:58,409
Is she planning to play some tricks again?

184
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,760
The Nether Demons in this place

185
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,020
have been cleared out.

186
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,680
Let's hurry to the Nameless Cliff.

187
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,960
We should strive to finish the mission tomorrow

188
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,040
and return immediately.

189
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,440
Right.

190
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,210
Xiaoxue,

191
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,160
you are right.

192
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:09,240
But

193
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,800
what about Danyu?

194
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,240
Let them go.

195
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,040
We have somewhere else to be.

196
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,370
It's not the same route.

197
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,280
I'm fine.

198
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,320
You guys go ahead.

199
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,720
I can take care of myself.

200
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,020
I'll wait for you here.

201
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,260
It really started.

202
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,040
Lu Danyu.

203
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,940
This is the middle of nowhere.

204
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:27,120
I advise you not to throw a temper tantrum in this situation.

205
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,000
If something happens,

206
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,760
no one will come back in time to save you.

207
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,400
Xiaoxue.

208
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,920
Danyu has grown up.

209
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,680
She doesn't have a child's temper anymore.

210
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,240
Besides,

211
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,560
she even said thank you just now,

212
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,159
and didn't speak so harshly.

213
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,560
Speaking harshly

214
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,040
and throwing temper tantrums.

215
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,240
What kind of character setting is this?

216
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,520
I am...

217
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,050
I'm really fine now.

218
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,130
Look.

219
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:49,720
You see.

220
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,320
Very well.

221
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:51,600
Don't worry.

222
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,300
Just go do your things.

223
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:54,690
Let's go.

224
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,160
They finally left.

225
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,360
Is this brother

226
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,920
a sis-con?

227
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,480
I need to be careful.

228
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,480
Don't break the character setting.

229
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:20,920
Oh, World Consciousness.

230
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:26,120
This world of yours is too amazing.

231
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:29,280
When I first came here, I felt like I was going to die.

232
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,120
But now...

233
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,760
After taking Mu Chenxue's medicine,

234
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,799
I feel like I could fly.

235
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,120
A healthy body.

236
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,440
How long has it been since I felt this way?

237
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,440
I really missed it.

238
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,200
Are you...

239
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,010
really okay?

240
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:45,940
I'm fine, I'm fine.

241
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,640
You've become more advanced.

242
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:50,640
Before, you were talking in my head.

243
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,120
Now you can change audio channels

244
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,560
and speak right in my ear.

245
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,080
I am right beside you.

246
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,040
What?
